content: The file will be moved to {{sectionName}} {{date}}

comment.text: The "SectionMoveNotification" translation key is used to display a notification message when a file is moved to a trash section. The message includes the section name and date of move, informing the user about the action taken on their file. This text appears in the UI as a tooltip when a deletion option is selected for a file in the "Quick Buttons" component.
